Play-offs.
The play-offs commenced following the conclusion of the 27-round regular season. To decide the grand finalists from the top eight finishing teams, Super League uses its unique &lt;a href="Super%20League%20play-offs"&gt;play-off system&lt;/a&gt;. The finals concluded with the &lt;a href="2011%20Super%20League%20Grand%20Final"&gt;2011 Super League Grand Final&lt;/a&gt;.
